sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Agent
    participant System

    User->>Agent: Submit Exercise Prompt
    loop Agent Reasoning Loop
        Agent-->>Agent: Plan / Reason ("What do I need to do?")
        Agent->>System: Execute action via tool (e.g., read_file / bash)
        System->>Agent: Tool response (e.g., file contents / stdout)
    end
    Agent->>User: Final Answer & Summary of Actions

    Note over User,System: Evaluation: Check tool usage count, time taken, final accuracy
